<p>My directory structure:</p>  <ol> <li><p>Com.Lib.db ( All db cfcs )</p></li> <li><p>Com.Lib.search ( All search cfcs )</p></li> <li><p>Com.Lib.utils ( All utils cfcs )</p></li> </ol>  <p>If I'm creating a normal object of (db) directory from webroot directory.</p>  <p>Example:</p>  <pre><code>Createobject("component", "Com.Lib.db.mycfcA"); </code></pre>  <p>If I'm in (db) directory creating object </p>  <p>Example:     Createobject("component", "mycfcA");</p>  <p>This is a normal case. In my case, I want to create an object from db directory to Utils OR Search. When I try to give full path for example: If I'm in the db directory, trying to create an object of myUtils.cfc, in the (Utils) Directory.</p>  <pre><code>Createobject("component", "Com.Lib.Utils. myUtils"); </code></pre>